query:
INSERT INTO market_order_backup (
    id,
    item_unique_name,
    location_id,
    quality_level,
    unit_price_silver,
    amount,
    auction_type,
    expires_at,
    updated_at)
SELECT DISTINCT ON (id)
    id,
    item_unique_name,
    location_id,
    quality_level,
    unit_price_silver,
    amount,
    auction_type,
    expires_at,
    updated_at
FROM UNNEST(
    $1::BIGINT[],
    $2::VARCHAR[],
    $3::VARCHAR[],
    $4::INT[],
    $5::INT[],
    $6::INT[],
    $7::VARCHAR[],
    $8::TIMESTAMPTZ[],
    $9::TIMESTAMPTZ[]) 
    AS market_order(
        id,
        item_unique_name,
        location_id,
        quality_level,
        unit_price_silver,
        amount,
        auction_type,
        expires_at,
        updated_at)
